        <Desc>VOTC, INC OFFERS A FLEXIBLE, MULTI-LEVEL OUTPATIENT PROGRAM FOR CLIENTS WHO ARE SEEKING EFFECTIVE TREATMENT FOR ADDICTIONS. OUTPATIENT SERVICES GIVE AN INDIVIDUAL THE OPPORTUNITY TO INTERACT IN A REAL WORLD ENVIRONMENT WHILE BENEFITTING FROM A PEER-ORIENTED, STRUCTURED THERAPEUTIC PROGRAM.</Desc>
